---
title: Spring Tortelloni Gratin with Basil Pesto & Asparagus
description: This skillet pasta bake truly is a one-pot-wonder – even the creamy pesto sauce thickens in the pan while the tortellini cook! A crispy topping of panko and Parmesan goes under the boiler for a few minutes until bubbly, browned, and irresistible.
